(20, 1, '2013-08-02 19:43:19', '2013-08-02 19:43:19', 'Still here! Its been a while since I last posted here, but at least any readers know i''m alive and well :D If you have noticed, I have changed the blog totally, goes for something a bit more simplistic and easier to read. Anyway, to give you an update of what I''ve been up to since your last read, its been almost 2 months since I arrived here. I am getting a little better at  Deutsch now, my lessons are doing me good. For instance (Funfzehn Guthaben fur Fonic mobil bitte) Is one I use too often when needing credit for my phone (its not cheap calling home).\r\n\r\nI''m really loving work now, getting a really good grip on how this industry runs in the real world, and not meaning like one of those ''group projects'' we did in second year. Like everyone helps you out no matter how busy they are or however many meetings they seem to have. Myself at the moment does not have many different things to be working on at the same time, but its picking up.\r\n\r\nI''m settled in now, and especially happy now I have my Blackberry Back! After having a nice swim in the sea with it, and getting it fixed for a cool 90 quid, it arrived this week and having the Internet on a phone has never been so good!\r\n\r\nMy landlady still does the old age trick of making me odd food and leaving it in my room for me, and likes replacing my washing up sponges at least 3 times a week aha. Little bit crazy.\r\n\r\nAnyway, it would be way too much effort to type a whole months worth of stuff. Here''s a nice picture of a postcard I sent home: ( My work place is the long building in the bottom left! )\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"> <a href="http://www.craighep.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/IMG_000002550.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-21" alt="My postcard sent to home (I work in the long building in the bottom left)" src="http://www.craighep.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/IMG_000002551.jpg" width="600" height="400" /></a></p>', 'I''m Back!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'im-back', '', '', '2013-08-02 19:58:15', '2013-08-02 19:58:15', '', 0, 'http://www.craighep.co.uk/blog/?p=20', 0, 'post', '', 0),
