(56, 1, '2013-08-05 20:52:09', '2013-08-05 20:52:09', '<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.craighep.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/P1010472.jpg"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-55" alt="" src="http://www.craighep.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/P1010472.jpg" width="700" height="550" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Okay, so I found out the time lapse function on my camera actually works tonight, from the same camera that had a nice dip in the sea when I was back in Aberystwyth, but this thing doesn''t know when to give up. So having taken this beautiful pic tonight I thought I should at least share it out there. I noticed how humidly warm it was tonight too, like this weather is hotter than English-hottest-day-of-the-year weather, and sleeping is definitely a problem now, so tonight I will watch films until my body makes me sleep. Then I won''t be at all tired for tomorrows day of work ;)</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Anyhow, the plan for tomorrow is to play some local badminton after work for a couple of hours then do some of my German homework. This time I have been asked to write a whole few sentences describing my family and who is what etc. If I can do this I''ll be German in no time!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Back tomorrow!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>', 'Germany by night', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'germany-by-night', '', '', '2013-08-05 21:02:12', '2013-08-05 21:02:12', '', 0, 'http://www.craighep.co.uk/blog/?p=56', 0, 'post', '', 0),
