(80, 1, '2013-08-31 20:33:43', '2013-08-31 20:33:43', 'Yes as the title shows, there''s not much to report today/ yesterday because really, all I have seemed to have done is watch lots of films or be in bed. After successfully being in work at half 8 everyday this week it defiantly caught up with me. Like even after a good 11 hour sleep last night, I still feel prepared to sleep forever. Anyway, other than them exciting happenings, I did manage to go for a quick bike ride today, found some random new roads in between farmers fields. I still don''t even know if i''m supposed to be on them. Guess I''ll find out the hard way if i''m not :P Also, Think I have the hang of recycling bottles here now, where for everyone you take back you get 25 cent. I know, you get loooads if you save them all. The other day I got a fiver from my bag of them :D You basically put each one on this weird conveyor belt thing in the shop and it goes in this tube where is spins until a scanner finds the bar code then continues through. Money falls out after you pres the big green button. No instructions required ;)\r\n\r\nLastly, tried my broken Blackberry today to see if by leaving it for a month and then using it now it would fix itself (Technology likes to do this). Amazingly after a few hours its still on and working, so I can even update this blog from that now! Less excuses for my poor amount of updates I guess...\r\n\r\nAnyway, see you soon!', 'Nothing much', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '79-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-08-31 20:33:43', '2013-08-31 20:33:43', '', 79, 'http://www.craighep.co.uk/blog/?p=80', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
