(97, 1, '2015-01-25 12:29:26', '2015-01-25 12:29:26', 'Decided I''d better start this today. This blog will be used throughout my dissertation, where i''ll be using it to log work and write any interesting findings. I''ll keep it to nice bullet points for each timed event, including this blog.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Blog created- 30 mins.</li>\r\n	<li>Github created- 5 mins.</li>\r\n	<li>Travis account created and linked to github- 5 mins.</li>\r\n	<li>Wrote initial project plan and outline- 2 hours.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIn short, my dissertation project is:\r\n<blockquote>Create a WebGL based application that calculates and visualises the OLAN(One letter aerobatic notation) catalogue in the form of a 3D plane performing aerobatic manoeuvres.</blockquote>\r\nCheck back for updates!', 'Beginning the Major Project', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'beginning-the-major-project', '', '', '2015-01-25 12:29:26', '2015-01-25 12:29:26', '', 0, 'http://www.craighep.co.uk/blog/?p=97', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(98, 1, '2015-01-25 12:29:26', '2015-01-25 12:29:26', 'Decided I''d better start this today. This blog will be used throughout my dissertation, where i''ll be using it to log work and write any interesting findings. I''ll keep it to nice bullet points for each timed event, including this blog.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Blog created- 30 mins.</li>\r\n	<li>Github created- 5 mins.</li>\r\n	<li>Travis account created and linked to github- 5 mins.</li>\r\n	<li>Wrote initial project plan and outline- 2 hours.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIn short, my dissertation project is:\r\n<blockquote>Create a WebGL based application that calculates and visualises the OLAN(One letter aerobatic notation) catalogue in the form of a 3D plane performing aerobatic manoeuvres.</blockquote>\r\nCheck back for updates!', 'Beginning the Major Project', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '97-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-25 12:29:26', '2015-01-25 12:29:26', '', 97, 'http://www.craighep.co.uk/blog/?p=98', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
