(102, 1, '2015-02-01 11:31:00', '2015-02-01 11:31:00', 'Since I missed out on the last two or three days, its best I do a collective log of work since then:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Tuesday 27th- A play with webGL, addition of some Three.js examples and modifications- 5 hours</li>\r\n	<li>Wednesday 28th- Document outlining my understandings of the OLAN notations, and calculations of primary manoeuvres- 4 hours</li>\r\n	<li>1st Feb- Starting of first report deadline, the outline of my project- 1 hour</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Work catch up log', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'work-catch-up-log', '', '', '2015-02-01 11:31:13', '2015-02-01 11:31:13', '', 0, 'http://www.craighep.co.uk/blog/?p=102', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(103, 1, '2015-02-01 11:31:00', '2015-02-01 11:31:00', 'Since I missed out on the last two or three days, its best I do a collective log of work since then:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Tuesday 27th- A play with webGL, addition of some Three.js examples and modifications- 5 hours</li>\r\n	<li>Wednesday 28th- Document outlining my understandings of the OLAN notations, and calculations of primary manoeuvres- 4 hours</li>\r\n	<li>1st Feb- Starting of first report deadline, the outline of my project- 1 hour</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Work catch up log', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '102-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-01 11:31:00', '2015-02-01 11:31:00', '', 102, 'http://www.craighep.co.uk/blog/?p=103', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(105, 1, '2015-02-02 16:17:45', '2015-02-02 16:17:45', 'Today:\r\nA project meeting with my supervisor- sounds like he really liked my previous document, which showed my understanding of the OLAN language which I''ll be using in my project. He did however now ask that I create a table detailing further each move, alongside all the possible pre and post-fixes that can be applied to each manoeuvre. He has also asked that I create some form of Gantt chart so that I can see exactly what and when I will be performing tasks.', 'Dissertation meeting and project specification documentation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '104-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-02 16:17:45', '2015-02-02 16:17:45', '', 104, 'http://www.craighep.co.uk/blog/?p=105', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(107, 1, '2015-02-02 16:19:28', '2015-02-02 16:19:28', 'Today:\r\nA project meeting with my supervisor- sounds like he really liked my previous document, which showed my understanding of the OLAN language which I''ll be using in my project. He did however now ask that I create a table detailing further each move, alongside all the possible pre and post-fixes that can be applied to each manoeuvre. He has also asked that I create some form of Gantt chart so that I can see exactly what and when I will be performing tasks.\r\n\r\nAnyhow:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Project meeting- including previous ones(since I forgot them)- 4 hours</li>\r\n	<li>Start and completion of first draft of project spec- 3 hours</li>\r\n	<li>Uploading of initial documentation to Github- 15 minutes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSee you tomorrow!', 'Dissertation meeting and project specification documentation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '104-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-02 16:19:28', '2015-02-02 16:19:28', '', 104, 'http://www.craighep.co.uk/blog/?p=107', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
